---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Security | personalai.cloud" description="Enterprise-grade security with end-to-end encryption, SOC 2, GDPR, and DPDP compliance. Your data stays yours.">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="mb-8">
      <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-stone-500">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-stone-900">Home</a></li>
        <li>/</li>
        <li class="text-stone-900 font-medium">Security</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Security & Privacy</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-stone-600 mb-10">Enterprise-grade protection with India-first compliance. Your data stays yours.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">🔐 End-to-End Encryption</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">All memory and messages are encrypted at rest and in transit using AES-256.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">🇮🇳 Data Residency</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Hosted in AWS Mumbai (ap-south-1). Your data never leaves India unless you choose otherwise.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">🛡️ SOC 2 & ISO 27001</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">We follow industry-standard security controls and are working toward SOC 2 certification.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">🚀 Self-Host Option</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Run the full stack on your infrastructure with Docker. 100% data control.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Compliance</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-12">
      <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-stone-200 bg-white text-sm">GDPR</span>
      <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-stone-200 bg-white text-sm">DPDP</span>
      <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-stone-200 bg-white text-sm">SOC 2</span>
      <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-stone-200 bg-white text-sm">ISO 27001</span>
      <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-stone-200 bg-white text-sm">HIPAA-ready</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Security Headers</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-3 text-stone-700 mb-10">
      <li>✅ HSTS with includeSubDomains</li>
      <li>✅ Content Security Policy (CSP)</li>
      <li>✅ X-Frame-Options: DENY</li>
      <li>✅ X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff</li>
      <li>✅ Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin</li>
      <li>✅ Permissions-Policy</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-white">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Report a Vulnerability</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-700 mb-6">We take security seriously. If you find a vulnerability, please report it responsibly.</p>
      <a href="mailto:security@personalai.cloud" class="inline-block bg-stone-900 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-stone-800 transition-colors">security@personalai.cloud</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
